name: <iter::adapters::filter::Filter<slice::iter::Split<'_, u8, str::IsAsciiWhitespace>, str::BytesIsNotEmpty> as iter::traits::iterator::Iterator>::map::<&str, str::UnsafeBytesToStr>

fn map<B, F>(self, f: F) -> Map<Self, F>
    where
        Self: Sized,
        F: FnMut(Self::Item) -> B,
    {
        Map::new(self, f)
    }
